name: Commercial real estate and offices and commercial premises collateral
description: Commercial real estate and offices and commercial premises collateral is Real estate collateral that is not Residential real estate collateral, as according to the Q&A 2014_1214 : “For the purposes of the CRR, "commercial immovable property" encompasses any immovable property that is not a "residential property" within the meaning of Article 4(1)(75) of the CRR”.
